<plot>A show about a group of vigilantes known as the Knights. Maldonado was the head of the group. Every week the Knights would go out and fight crime in their Varsity jackets with two basic rules: 1)No excessive violence and 2)No killing. In the first episode, one of the members broke those rules and was sent to prison.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?294699</url></doc>
